high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter after the refrigerator.
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the counter.
Turn left, move to the front of the refrigerator.
Slice the lettuce in the refrigerator.
Move to the front of the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Move to the front of the refrigerator.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, move to the counter at the sink.
Put slice of lettuce in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter between the stove and the trash bin.
Put slice of lettuce on counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed piece of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn to the right. Then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around and step to the left. Turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and slice the lettuce.
Open and then shut the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge.
Open the fridge again.
Take a slice of lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn around complete and walk forward to the sink. Turn right to face the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce in the sink and wash it. Take the slice out.
Turn to the left and walk forward then make another left to face the counter.
Place the slice of lettuce on the shelf.
Cross the room, hang a right at the fridge and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the knife to the left of the green sponge on the counter.
Turn around, hang a right at the counter and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Open the upper part of the fridge, slice the head of lettuce on the bottom shelf and close the door.
Look down at the lower part of the black fridge.
Open the fridge, put the knife inside on the top shelf in front of the lettuce and close the door.
Look at the upper part of the fridge door.
Open the fridge, pick up a slice of lettuce from the bottom shelf and close the door.
Turn around and hang a right at the counter to face the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds, and pick it back up.
Turn around and turn right at the end of the counter near the stove.
Place the chilled slice of lettuce on the edge of the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of lettuce on a counter.
